title: Why Food Prep Ahead of Time is Key!
itunes:title: Why Food Prep Ahead of Time is Key!
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

During this live you will hear me talk about how I roll on Sundays. I broke this episode into two parts. First I talked to you from my car after hitting the store and preparing for a workout.

Then after I am done cooking and cleaning we talk about my food prep and why I believe in it so much. I know that having a plan and being willing to prep ahead of time is a KEY factor in my ability to keep off 100lbs.

This episode will teach you where to start.
